# VHS tape for sracha get command
Output docs/images/get.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "Fira Code"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 500
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set LineHeight 1.2
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 10

Type "sracha get SRR28588231"
Enter
Sleep 30s
